&gt;&gt; Richard Comeaux: She says yeah

00:25:02.980 --> 00:25:04.280
and she just plays it
for me right there.

00:25:04.280 --> 00:25:05.580
Right there.

00:25:05.580 --> 00:25:06.880
So, we kind of map it out.

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:08.180
Then we play it.

00:25:08.180 --> 00:25:09.480
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: Yeah.

00:25:09.480 --> 00:25:10.780
Yeah.

00:25:10.780 --> 00:25:12.080
&gt;&gt; Beau Thomas: It's great.

00:25:12.080 --> 00:25:13.380
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: So, that was sort

00:25:13.380 --> 00:25:14.680
of my next question was how do
you guys then take, you know?

00:25:14.680 --> 00:25:15.980
&gt;&gt; Richard Comeaux:
Just like I just said.

00:25:15.980 --> 00:25:17.280
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: Just like that?

00:25:17.280 --> 00:25:18.580
&gt;&gt; Richard Comeaux:
T, I got a new song.

