&gt;&gt; Beau Thomas: It's like FTD
flower arrangements while you wait,

00:25:19.880 --> 00:25:21.180
you know?

00:25:21.180 --> 00:25:22.480
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: Right.

00:25:22.480 --> 00:25:23.780
&gt;&gt; Beau Thomas: We just
put it all together.

00:25:23.780 --> 00:25:25.080
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: As
a matter of fact,

00:25:25.080 --> 00:25:26.380
when we were doing sound check
earlier, Beau had never heard,

00:25:26.380 --> 00:25:28.550
I had put the new waltz
that I had wrote,

00:25:28.550 --> 00:25:32.570
or that came out just a couple days
ago, and Beau had never heard it.

00:25:32.570 --> 00:25:33.870
And I said, "OK.

00:25:33.870 --> 00:25:35.170
If we have time, we're
going to do it today."

00:25:35.170 --> 00:25:39.200
So, I just start playing it and
they'll just, as a matter fact,

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:40.910
on the plane, I told
him on the plane.

00:25:40.910 --> 00:25:42.210
&gt;&gt; Beau Thomas: Yeah.

00:25:42.210 --> 00:25:43.510
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: I had
recorded it on the voice memo.

00:25:43.510 --> 00:25:45.630
And so he was listening
to it on the voice memo.

00:25:45.630 --> 00:25:46.930
And he goes, "What key is it in?"

00:25:46.930 --> 00:25:48.230
And I said, "It's in E."

00:25:48.230 --> 00:25:49.530 position:56%
And I could see him doing like this.

00:25:49.530 --> 00:25:52.630
He goes, "I'm learning
it right now."

00:25:52.630 --> 00:25:54.560
So [multiple speakers].

00:25:54.560 --> 00:25:55.860
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: All right.

