would come down and snatch you up

00:41:58.540 --> 00:42:01.040
and you would never be seen again.

00:42:01.040 --> 00:42:02.450
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: Right.

00:42:02.450 --> 00:42:03.750
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: Yeah.

00:42:03.750 --> 00:42:05.050
Happy little children stories.

00:42:05.050 --> 00:42:06.350
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: Yeah.

00:42:06.350 --> 00:42:08.120
Well, you know, sometimes those
can be useful [multiple speakers].

00:42:08.120 --> 00:42:09.420
&gt;&gt; Yvette Landry: Absolutely.

00:42:09.420 --> 00:42:10.720
Absolutely.

00:42:10.720 --> 00:42:12.020
So.

00:42:12.020 --> 00:42:13.320
&gt;&gt; Steve Winick: All right.

