00:43:48.010 --> 00:43:49.310
I don't know.

00:43:49.310 --> 00:43:50.610
It's just scary.

00:43:50.610 --> 00:43:53.080 position:56%
It's scary that nobody is coming up.

00:43:53.080 --> 00:43:55.200
Now, they attempt it.

00:43:55.200 --> 00:43:58.860
And spent thousands of dollars.

00:43:58.860 --> 00:44:00.160
