00:44:02.870 --> 00:44:05.050
under the bed and it rots there.

00:44:05.050 --> 00:44:10.090
So, you know, it's an instrument
that, you know, you've got to fall

00:44:10.090 --> 00:44:12.080
in love with like I
did right out the gate.

00:44:12.080 --> 00:44:13.880 position:56%
You know, you got to, I went to bed,

00:44:13.880 --> 00:44:16.910
I remember with that thing
right next to my bed.

00:44:16.910 --> 00:44:19.740
And I looked at it like I am
going to learn this thing.

00:44:19.740 --> 00:44:21.830
But you have to marry it.

00:44:21.830 --> 00:44:24.720
And you have to be
willing to sacrifice.

00:44:24.720 --> 00:44:26.810
Because it doesn't come easy.

00:44:26.810 --> 00:44:29.390
It's the hands, the
feet, or the legs.

00:44:29.390 --> 00:44:31.250
It doesn't come easy.

00:44:31.250 --> 00:44:35.910
So, but if you work hard, it's
a shame it takes this long,

00:44:35.910 --> 00:44:39.270
but you know, you can reap some
of the rewards, but what we talked

00:44:39.270 --> 00:44:44.070
